<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar', { page }) %>
    <main class="page services-page">
      <header>
        <h1>Services tailored to your goals</h1>
        <p>Choose one or combine several â€” we adapt to your roadmap.</p>
      </header>
      <section class="service-list">
        <article>
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/20/400/250" alt="Product Discovery" class="service-img">
          <div class="service-content">
            <h2>Product Discovery</h2>
            <p>
              Workshops, user interviews, and rapid prototyping sessions that uncover real user
              problems and validate market fit before we write a single line of code.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article>
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/3/400/250" alt="Custom Development" class="service-img">
          <div class="service-content">
            <h2>Custom Development</h2>
            <p>
              Cross-functional squads delivering web apps, APIs, and integrations using battle-tested
              processes, CI/CD pipelines, and transparent reporting cadences.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article>
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/6/400/250" alt="Growth & Care" class="service-img">
          <div class="service-content">
            <h2>Growth & Care</h2>
            <p>
              Post-launch optimization, A/B testing, performance tuning, and long-term maintenance SLAs
              to keep your platform fast and secure.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
      <section class="process-timeline">
        <p class="eyebrow">How we work</p>
        <h2>The sprint rhythm that keeps teams aligned</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <span class="step-index">01</span>
            <h3>Research & Align</h3>
            <p>Stakeholder interviews, tech audits, and analytics deep dives uncover the real constraints.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <span class="step-index">02</span>
            <h3>Co-create</h3>
            <p>Design + engineering pair to prototype, validate, and adjust scope in tight feedback loops.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <span class="step-index">03</span>
            <h3>Build & Automate</h3>
            <p>Modular code, CI/CD, and observability baked in from sprint one for confident releases.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <span class="step-index">04</span>
            <h3>Launch & Evolve</h3>
            <p>Progressive rollouts, experimentation, and growth playbooks ensure the product keeps compounding.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="toolkit">
        <p class="eyebrow">Favorite stack</p>
        <h2>Choosing the right tools for every challenge</h2>
        <div class="badge-wrap">
          <span class="badge">Node.js</span>
          <span class="badge">Express</span>
          <span class="badge">Next.js</span>
          <span class="badge">TypeScript</span>
          <span class="badge">PostgreSQL</span>
          <span class="badge">Tailwind</span>
          <span class="badge">AWS</span>
          <span class="badge">Docker</span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
